tactic: destruct H1 as [H1 | H1], H2 as [H2 | H2].
exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 0 branches.

original: intros P Q H1 H2. destruct H1 as [H1 | H1], H2 as [H2 | H2]. - left. apply H1. - left. apply H1. - left. apply H2. - right. intro contra. destruct contra as [contra1 contra2]. destruct H1. split; auto.
